{"tid":677434,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［容我張狂］一百米既肉燥飯堅正，平均$40蚊一餐(大埔J)","createTime":"2018-05-25T07:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T15:20:52.000Z","uid":188198,"like":11,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8b0426be709f5da353879aae71d128bb89094e91","tid":677434,"uid":188198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:39:33.000Z","msg":"Lunch平均$40蚊一個餐，但味道遠遠超出佢個價錢，性價比十足👍🏻。<br />\n講番今日個lunch，我叫左糖醋排骨 拼 肉燥飯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/151930_6659216e1044bfcb062e565d0240546e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F151930_6659216e1044bfcb062e565d0240546e.png&h=ab3dc359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好睇佢細細隻碗，但食完呢個餐，包你飽到放工。<br />\n<br />\n糖醋骨非常入味，醋味唔會過酸，甜酸比例恰到好處，肉質亦不過不失（對得住佢呢個價錢）。<br />\n<br />\n講番今日個重點，肉燥飯，你每食一啖都有種&lsquo;LimLim&rsquo;地既感覺，而且佢比既肉燥份量係夠你撈成碗飯，而我亦都懷疑佢係加左豬油落去，所以我淨係用筷子都夾到佢一團團既飯。<br />\n<br />\n至於飲品方面，本身包杯熱飲，轉台式飲品就加$8蚊，但其實你食完佢碗飯，個胃都擺唔落杯珍珠奶茶。"},{"pid":"06e76958937dad6eccf147903cf949d53d101214","tid":677434,"uid":146063,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:44:58.000Z","msg":"打手"},{"pid":"47725ee1efff593ee1779e46f7b2883de9577a06","tid":677434,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:45:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a658eb399571e7c13b34f275527327d27f8e348f","tid":677434,"uid":4813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"666622079b210ede87093d1779a1865b83988e52","tid":677434,"uid":92042,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:47:18.000Z","msg":"打手味濃"},{"pid":"1f6c0a408d64588f30600ae9d329718fb526146f","tid":677434,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:49:07.000Z","msg":"你嘔完?"},{"pid":"191202d1abe84182126c6afbf34a321d2e44a811","tid":677434,"uid":188198,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:52:10.000Z","msg":"漏左講隻蛋，佢呢間另一出名就係佢個滷水汁，而佢隻蛋係非常之入味，完完全全食到佢隻汁，而我亦都試過佢其他滷水產品，豆腐，大腸，矮瓜等等，都係非常出色，值得一試。"},{"pid":"9a76cd04eac17240ec963d94841eecec00370e25","tid":677434,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:52:45.000Z","msg":"d肉燥咁水既？濕得濟啊ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b1d4e67d97e58222765764bceeda9594e2fdc5","tid":677434,"uid":188198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"666622079b210ede87093d1779a1865b83988e52","tid":677434,"uid":92042,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:47:18.000Z","msg":"打手味濃"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:57:59.000Z","msg":"係我大埔做野，發覺好多美食，要share一下，黎緊陸續有來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6075451c3cce433de02c611a76e43846f724305b","tid":677434,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T08:50:34.000Z","msg":"汁飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e73ae179e81bf8ea13967fdf0a30db259b482a6","tid":677434,"uid":12757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"59b1d4e67d97e58222765764bceeda9594e2fdc5","tid":677434,"uid":188198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"666622079b210ede87093d1779a1865b83988e52","tid":677434,"uid":92042,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:47:18.000Z","msg":"打手味濃"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:57:59.000Z","msg":"係我大埔做野，發覺好多美食，要share一下，黎緊陸續有來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T08:54:14.000Z","msg":"聽聞<br />\n大埔既美食比領展迫走哂咁滯<br />\n依家果d只係無咩人去 冇咩客 所以冇點加租果d"},{"pid":"0b5950cdba32298e536534e914058279fb690ff7","tid":677434,"uid":129660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T08:55:30.000Z","msg":"你篇文帶有濃濃既打手味。"},{"pid":"3198fd115c3a0fd00142969324575983f072d70e","